/* First get AGN objects with their r-band stats showing variability */ WITH agn_r_var AS
  (SELECT p.oid,
          p.probability,
          m.ndet AS r_ndet,
          m.magsigma AS r_magsigma
   FROM probability p
   INNER JOIN magstat m ON p.oid = m.oid
   WHERE p.ranking = 1
     AND p.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
     AND p.class_name = 'AGN'
     AND m.fid = 2 /* r band */
     AND m.ndet > 0
     AND m.magsigma > 0 ), /* Get g-band stats for these objects */ agn_g_stats AS
  (SELECT p.oid,
          m.ndet AS g_ndet,
          m.magsigma AS g_magsigma
   FROM probability p
   INNER JOIN magstat m ON p.oid = m.oid
   WHERE p.oid IN
       (SELECT oid
        FROM agn_r_var)
     AND m.fid = 1 /* g band */ ) /* Combine and filter based on g-band conditions */
SELECT a.oid,
       a.probability,
       a.r_ndet,
       a.r_magsigma,
       COALESCE(g.g_ndet, 0) AS g_ndet,
       COALESCE(g.g_magsigma, 0) AS g_magsigma
FROM agn_r_var a
LEFT JOIN agn_g_stats g ON a.oid = g.oid
WHERE g.g_ndet = 0
  OR g.g_magsigma = 0
ORDER BY probability ASC,
         r_ndet ASC,
         r_magsigma ASC,
         g_ndet ASC,
         g_magsigma ASC,
         oid ASC

  (SELECT p.oid,
          p.probability,
          mr.ndet AS r_ndet,
          mr.magsigma AS r_magsigma,
          mg.ndet AS g_ndet,
          mg.magsigma AS g_magsigma
   FROM probability p
   INNER JOIN magstat mr ON p.oid = mr.oid
   AND mr.fid = 2 /* r band */
   LEFT JOIN magstat mg ON p.oid = mg.oid

   WHERE p.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'
     AND p.ranking = 1
     AND p.class_name = 'AGN'
     AND mr.ndet > 0 /* has detections in r */
     AND mr.magsigma > 0 /* shows variability in r */

          OR mg.magsigma = 0)/* no detections or no variability in g */ )
SELECT *
FROM agn_objects
ORDER BY oid ASC;
